Class OneOperandInstruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.Instruction
      • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.OneOperandInstruction

  • public class OneOperandInstruction
extends Instruction
    A OneOperandInstruction is an instruction that is known to have only one operand.
